== 新闻事业 ==

2017年3月，他成为《{{le|伦敦标准晚报|London Evening Standard}}》的侯任主编，当年5月正式就任。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/george-osborne-announced-as-new-evening-standard-editor-a3492361.html|title=George Osborne announced as new Evening Standard editor|newspaper=Evening Standard|accessdate=2017-11-28|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404221950/http://www.standard.co.uk/news/london/george-osborne-announced-as-new-evening-standard-editor-a3492361.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于但是他还是国会议员，所以这样的兼职受到一些人批评，有议员担心利益冲突以及有辱议员之体，也有人称奥斯本新闻历练不足。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-39304944|title=George Osborne to edit London newspaper|date=2017-03-17|newspaper=BBC News|accessdate=2017-11-28|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123104816/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-39304944|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也被指责违反{{le|商业任用咨询委员会|Advisory Committee on Business Appointments}}的关于前大臣就业的规则，未经委员会的同意接受主编一职。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/mar/18/george-osborne-accused-of-breaching-rules-with-evening-standard-job|title=George Osborne accused of breaching rules with Evening Standard job|last=Mason|first=Rowena|date=2017-03-18|last2=Gayle|first2=Damien|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2017-11-28|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125131918/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/mar/18/george-osborne-accused-of-breaching-rules-with-evening-standard-job|dead-url=no}}</ref>

时事讽刺杂志《{{le|第三只眼 (杂志)|Private Eye|第三只眼}}》披露了《伦敦标准晚报》老板{{le|叶甫根尼·列别杰夫|Evgeny Lebedev}}与奥斯本的关系。奥斯本任财政大臣时，经常承诺向“标准慈善运动”拨款。如2015年他提议读者为伦敦标准晚报的{{le|大奥蒙德街医院|Great Ormond Street Hospital}}倡议捐款150万英镑。这份报纸在2015年伦敦最有影响力的“时代潮头1000人”评比中将奥斯本列为第一。奥斯本在财政大臣任内未能解决有利于非英国国居民税收状况，列别杰夫被认为受益于此，而列别杰夫的报纸在[[2015年英国大选|2015年大选]]和{{le|2016年大伦敦市长选举|London mayoral election, 2016}}中都强烈支持[[保守黨_(英國)|保守党]]。<ref>{{cite magazine |last= |first= |date=24 March 2017 |title=St. George lowers the Standard |url= |magazine={{le|第三只眼|Private Eye}} |location=London |publisher=Pressdram Ltd }}</ref>

