2017-11-21|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919144248/https://www.standard.co.uk/comment/comment/evening-standard-comment-pm-s-action-on-modern-slavery-deserves-credit-a3638276.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

